Time taken to complete: 5 hours

Running the code:
make clean
make
./hw2

Keyboard Interaction:
0       ---> Reset view angle
m       ---> Adjust perspective between orthogonal, perspective, and first person
x       ---> Adjust axis
arrows  ---> Change view angle (only in orthogonal and perspective mode)
a,s,w,d ---> Move in first person (forward/backward/left/right)
j,k,i,l ---> Look in first person (left/down/up/right)
-/+     ---> Toggle Field of View
ESC     ---> Exit
